V0603_01_00_00_0.text:
Let's do this!
Mano a mano!

V0603_01_00_01_0.text: You think you can flex on me with those tiny muscles?

V0603_01_00_02_0.text: The Gore's the #1 Celebrity Duelist in LINK VRAINS!

V0603_01_00_03_0.text: You may talk a good game, but can you play one?

V0603_01_00_04_0.text: Everyone I'm facing is goin' down for the three count!

V0603_01_00_05_0.text: I'm the top dog in LINK VRAINS - not you, Playmaker!

V0603_01_00_06_0.text:
Blue Angel!
Let's see who's the real #1 Celebrity Duelist!

V0603_01_00_07_0.text: If you're gonna risk it all, so will I, Soulburner!

V0603_01_00_08_0.text: You picked the wrong bounty to hunt!

V0603_01_00_09_0.text: You won't tear down everything I built, Varis!

V0603_01_00_10_0.text: Loosen up that tie and let's get Duelin', Zaizen!

V0603_01_00_11_0.text: I won't let you take LINK VRAINS from the kids!

V0603_01_00_11_1.text: You mess with the horns, you're gonna get gored!

V0603_03_00_00_0.text: It's time I stop playin' and pin you 1-2-3!

V0603_03_00_01_0.text: Showing off against me is gonna cost you everything!!

V0603_03_00_04_0.text:
Heh heh heh...
Time to show my stuff!

V0603_03_00_05_0.text: The bigger the comeback, the bigger the hero!

V0603_05_00_00_0.text:
Your time in the spotlight's up!
I'm in charge now!

V0603_06_01_01_0.text: This is what I was waiting for!

V0603_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0603_07_09_01_0.text: This is the card I Set!

V0603_10_00_00_0.text: I'm bringin' this monster to the melee!

V0603_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0603_11_10_02_1.text:
I set my monsters in the Link Arrows!
Link the circuit!

V0603_11_10_03_0.text: Time to crank up my circuit!

V0603_11_10_04_0.text: Time to crank up my circuit!

V0603_11_10_04_1.text:
I set my monsters in the Link Arrows!
Link the circuit!

V0603_21_00_00_0.text:
You're tough.
I thought I'd knock you out by now.

V0603_21_00_01_0.text: You're getting gored by The Gore!

V0603_21_00_03_0.text:
You stronger than this?
Then show me!

V0603_21_00_04_0.text:
Heh...
I'm just gettin' warmed up!

V0603_21_00_05_0.text:
Knockin' me down ain't hard.
Keepin' me down is!

V0603_28_00_00_0.text: You like the way I put on a poundin'?

V0603_28_00_01_0.text:
I'm always ready for a rematch!
Rooooooar!

V0603_28_00_02_0.text:
You've given your life to Dueling.
But so have I!

V0603_28_00_03_0.text: No matter how many times I fall, I always get back up!

V0603_28_00_03_1.text: Cuz I can't let the kids in the orphanage down!

V0603_28_00_04_0.text:
See that?
I adapt to any type of Duel you dish out!

V0603_28_00_05_0.text: Like the dinos of old, The Gore always evolves his game!

V0603_28_00_06_0.text: I'm rising in the ranks to become the #1 Celebrity Duelist!

V0603_29_00_01_0.text: You didn't even break a sweat...

V0603_29_00_02_0.text:
I'll pin you for the three count someday!
That's a promise!

V0603_29_00_03_0.text:
I lost...
How am I gonna show my face to the kids...

V0603_29_00_04_0.text: There are these kids who look up to me.

V0603_29_00_04_1.text: That's why I have to get up - so they won't look down on me!

V0603_29_00_05_0.text:
No one wins every time.
We all gotta lose someday.

V0603_29_00_05_1.text:
But will losing fuel me or break me?
That's the true test.

V0603_33_00_03_0.text:
See this bicep?
That's where the power comes from!

V0603_33_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Skill!
Pain and Gain!

V0603_33_00_07_0.text:
I'll evolve my Duel with this Skill!
Dinowrestle Revolution!

V0603_30_00_00_0.text: This is how I put on a show!

V0603_30_00_01_0.text: Let's pump up the crowd and send 'em home happy!

V0603_30_00_02_0.text: You took my attack on purpose to make things exciting!?

V0603_34_00_00_0.text: You act like a hero, but you're nothin' but a zero!

V0603_34_00_01_0.text: Want me to pin you for the 3 count or KO you for the 10?

V0603_34_00_02_0.text: The crowd wants to see our best monsters fight!

V0603_34_00_04_0.text: If you're playin' no holds barred, it's time for Grim Gore!

V0603_34_00_05_0.text: Grim Gore's all about servin' up pain with a heap o' defeat!

V0603_34_00_06_0.text: This will make you tap out!

V0603_34_00_08_0.text: Instead of showboatin', I'm going for the win!

V0603_34_00_09_0.text: You worried my brain's gonna short circuit?

V0603_34_00_11_0.text: I removed my brain chip. Fusing with an AI was a bad idea.

V0603_32_00_01_0.text:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links!
It's time to link into the VRAINS!

V0603_35_00_00_0.text:
I'm The Gore!
The heavyweight champ of LINK VRAINS!

V0603_36_00_00_0.text: Go pin 'em for the three count!

V0603_36_00_01_0.text:
I'm tagging you in!
Do your thing!

I activate my Spell Card!
